Dialogue: 0,0:00:11.09,0:00:13.62,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長 學長
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.86,0:00:19.75,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,筒隱 早上好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.27,0:00:22.35,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,竟然在這種地方睡著了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.86,0:00:24.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我一直在找你
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.30,0:00:25.40,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,抱歉抱歉
Dialogue: 0,0:00:25.82,0:00:28.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,你看 畢竟發生了那種事情
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.01,0:00:30.06,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我也不好繼續待在那房間裡了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:30.50,0:00:32.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,那種事情…嗎？
Dialogue: 0,0:00:36.83,0:00:39.18,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,昨晚的那個…那個…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.51,0:00:41.25,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,下次再偷窺我的話
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.47,0:00:43.45,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,我真的要生氣了
Dialogue: 0,0:00:43.62,0:00:44.66,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,遵…遵命！
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.27,0:00:46.57,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,能明白就好
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.80,0:00:51.77,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,學長
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.46,0:00:54.50,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這個倉庫裡到底…
Dialogue: 0,0:00:56.01,0:00:58.01,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,希望你不要嚇一跳
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.37,0:01:00.16,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,這裡是我的房間
Dialogue: 0,0:01:00.33,0:01:02.13,Default,NTP,0000,0000,0000,,不…是我的家

